These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, malaysian, japanese, turkish, german, russian, colombian
1. the malaysian is in the middle##1
2. the malaysian is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the german is on the right of the turkish##1
4. the indonesian is on the right of the japanese##1
5. the colombian is on the far left##1
6. the russian is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | colombian | turkish | german | malaysian | japanese | indonesian | russian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  videographer, photographer, pilot, engineer, coach, social-worker, musician
1. the musician is on the far right##1
2. the videographer is on the far left##1
3. the videographer is on the left of the coach##1
4. the coach is on the left of the pilot##1
5. the engineer is on the right of the social-worker##1
6. the musician is on the right of the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | videographer | coach | pilot | social-worker | engineer | photographer | musician |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, baking, puzzles, filmmaking, traveling, gardening, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | traveling | camping | gardening | puzzles | skydiving | baking | filmmaking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-4::.
