.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-5::.
7 different pets are kept: horse, goat, frog, fish, rabbit, bird, pony
1. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | pony | frog | fish | bird | horse | goat | rabbit |

