.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: family, mystery, time-travel, adventure, action, romance, western
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | action | mystery | family | romance | adventure | western | time-travel |

